HEADWORD: Ignorantly
<hw>Ig"no*rant*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a ignorant manner;
without knowledge; inadvertently.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Whom therefoer ye <qex>ignorantly</qex> worship, him declare I
unto you.</q> <rj><qau>Acts xvii. 23.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

